                      CHAPTER 231</span></div></div><br clear="all"/><div id="title"><span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:0.9em;">An act to amend Sections 17024.5, 17052.6, 17052.12, 17053.91, 17062, 17063, 17076, 17085, 17087.5, 17131.4, 17131.8, 17140, 17140.3, 17144.5, 17201.6, 17204, 17220, 17225, 17241, 17250, 17255, 17270, 17271, 17276, 17323, 17501, 17551, 17559, 17560.5, 17564, 18031.5, 18036, 18042, 18409, 18622.5, 18631.7, 18666, 19058, 19141.5, 19144, 19167, 19183, 19852, 19900, 23400, 23453, 23455, 23456, 23609, 23691, 23711, 23806, 23809, 24308.6, 24344, 24349.1, 24356, 24357, 24358, 24365, 24416, 24440, 24459, 24465, 24601, 24661.5, 24661.6, 24673.2, 24721,
		  and 24990.5 of, to amend and repeal
